mission_june_july_2015_-_aden_taiz-1.jpg\" alt=\"A joint crisis\/MENA mission to Yemen in June\/July 2015. Photos are from the team's visits to Taiz and Aden.  On 7 July, just after mid-afternoon (asr) prayers, a coalition strike killed 11 worshippers and injured several others in a mosque in Waht, a village north of Aden in Lahj governorate.\" \/><figcaption class=\"figcaption--article\"><span class=\"credits\">\u00a9 \u56fd\u9645\u7279\u8d66\u7ec4\u7ec7<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure class=\"figure--article\"><img class=\"image--fullwidth\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/225714_yemen_-_saudi_led_airstrikes_hit_yemen_s_capital.jpg\" alt=\"Yemenis search for the air attack victims around the destroyed buildings after Saudi-led airstrikes hit Sanaa's Old City, Yemen, on June 04, 2015.\" \/><figcaption class=\"figcaption--article\"><span class=\"credits\">\u00a9 Mohammed Hamoud\/Anadolu Agency\/Getty Images<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure class=\"figure--article\"><img class=\"image--fullwidth\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/228052.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><figcaption class=\"figcaption--article\"><span class=\"credits\">\u00a9 \u56fd\u9645\u7279\u8d66\u7ec4\u7ec7<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure class=\"figure--article\"><img class=\"image--fullwidth\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/226425.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><figcaption class=\"figcaption--article\"><span class=\"credits\">\u00a9 Rawan Shaif<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"col col--1\/12--md not--sm\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"col col--5\/12--md\">\n<div class=\"col__content wysiwyg\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<h2>\u5404\u65b9\u4fb5\u72af\u4eba\u6743\u7684\u884c\u5f84<\/h2>\n<p>\u56fd\u9645\u7279\u8d66\u7ec4\u7ec7<a href=\"https:\/\/www.amnesty.org\/en\/documents\/mde31\/2291\/2015\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\u641c\u96c6\u5230\u7684\u8bc1\u636e<\/a>\u63ed\u793a\u51fa\uff0c\u6b64\u6b21\u4ea4\u6218\u7684\u5404\u65b9